        "subject": "LU-5483 tests: perform recovery-mds-scale test",
        "message": "LU-5483 tests: perform recovery-mds-scale test\n\nThis is for test only.\n\nRevert \"LU-5203 zfs: Update spl/zfs version to 0.6.3\"\nThis reverts commit 3372e7bf6c9672a5b62f0a2531e3c5463f877fdb.\n\nRevert \"LU-4606 utils: Mount uses so for backing fstype\"\nThis reverts commit 0d77156572c2b77581f01d960c0e5738b369de6a.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly alwaysuploadlogs \\\nenvdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes,REQFAIL=100,DURATION=28800 \\\nmdtfilesystemtype=ldiskfs mdsfilesystemtype=ldiskfs ostfilesystemtype=ldiskfs \\\nclientdistro=el6 ossdistro=el6 mdsdistro=el6 clientarch=x86_64 \\\nossarch=x86_64 mdsarch=x86_64 clientcount=4 osscount=2 mdscount=2 \\\nmdssizegb=10 ostsizegb=10 austeroptions=-R failover=true iscsi=1 \\\ntestlist=recovery-mds-scale\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I63fc6202d753d8fb94d05224f04e68d05ab0cfd9\n"
      },
